---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import AffiliateButton from '../../components/AffiliateButton.astro';

const title = "Future Kind versus Performance Lab: Which Sleep Aid Actually Works in 2026";
const description = "We analyze the physiological impact of Future Kind and Performance Lab sleep formulas to see which natural sleep aid will truly help you wake up feeling refreshed.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <article>
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-4 block font-semibold">Sleep & Recovery Comparison</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          Future Kind versus Performance Lab: Which Sleep Aid Actually Works?
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
          <span class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Editorial Review</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Updated May 2026</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700">
        <p class="lead text-xl italic text-slate-900 mb-8" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          Quality sleep is the ultimate foundation of health. Without it, even the best nutrition and brain boosters fail. In 2026, the market is flooded with sleep aids, but two formulas stand out for their natural, non-habit-forming approach: Future Kind and Performance Lab.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-10">
          At Wellness Sanctuary, we analyze the physiological impact of these ingredients to see which one will truly help you wake up feeling refreshed.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">1. The Science of Rest</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-8 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Future Kind (Sleep)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            Focuses on a synergistic blend of herbal extracts (Valerian, Chamomile) and a low dose of Melatonin. It is designed for those who have trouble falling asleep due to a racing mind.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-12 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Performance Lab (Sleep)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            Takes a different approach by focusing on Natural Melatonin from Montmorency Tart Cherry and Magnesium. It aims to optimize the body's natural sleep cycles and muscle relaxation without using synthetic hormones.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">2. Comparison Table</h2>
        
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-slate-900">
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Future Kind (Sleep)</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Performance Lab (Sleep)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Main Ingredient</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Melatonin + Herbal Blend</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Magnesium + Tart Cherry</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Approach</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Sedative & Calming</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Circadian Rhythm Support</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Non-GMO / Vegan</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Yes</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Yes</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Next-Day Grogginess</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Low</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">None</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Best For</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Occasional Insomnia</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Long-term Sleep Quality</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">3. Our Editorial Verdict</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-900 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Future Kind if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You need immediate help falling asleep after a stressful day and prefer a formula that includes traditional calming herbs like Lemon Balm and Passionflower.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="future-kind" text="Try Future Kind" />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-600 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Performance Lab if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You want to improve your overall sleep architecture and recovery without relying on synthetic melatonin. It is the perfect choice for athletes and high-performers.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="performance-lab" text="Try Performance Lab" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12" />

        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-200">
          <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🩺</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Wellness Insight</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8">
            A sleep aid is only as good as your Sleep Hygiene. For the best results, we recommend pairing these supplements with a blue-light-free environment 30 minutes before bed.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Need a personalized recovery plan?</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-6">
            Take our Rest & Recovery Quiz to find the supplement that matches your specific lifestyle and stress levels.
          </p>
          <a href="/quiz" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-all shadow-md">
            Find My Program
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
